replies.body:
There's been word of a Taric remake ("LoL's Paladin") for a while, but it hasn't been mentioned in any specifics. So, while we know there's plans, and they'll keep him outrageous, we don't know exactly what'll happen.
As of now, there's sometimes teams in which Taric fits amazingly - and yeah, he _is_ a badashe paladin with a hammer. In his own way.

{{champion:44}}
